    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Cut your <strong>halloumi</strong> into 3 slices per person</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halloumi</strong> <strong>slices</strong> and cook for 1-2 min on each side or until golden</p>",
